data.description: Country living yet close to town!  Bring the horses and toys! Private setting located at the end of dead end road!  This home has an open split floorpan with 3 bedroom and 2 baths. The large kitchen has a large island and seating, formal living area and a unique sunken additional living room or dining room featuring a cozy fireplace.  Outside there is beautiful landscaped lawn area, mare motel and a large 2 car carport w/ attached shop.  The carport could easily be converted to a closed garage.  Plenty of room for parking, trailers, toys and even an area for a small arena.
